response.overview: 'No Angel' chronicles Jay Dobyns’ unprecedented undercover operation infiltrating the inner circle of the Hells Angels Motorcycle Club from 2001-03 in Operation Black Biscuit — an immersion so complete it blurred identity, endangered loved ones and demanded choices with lifelong consequences. Dobyns was the first federal agent to infiltrate the inner circle of the outlaw biker gang. His aim was simple: to examine the criminal underbelly of the Hells Angels and bring a major case against them. The film follows Dobyns as he’s on the brink of losing himself and lifts the lid on one of the world’s most infamous underworlds.
response.title: No Angel
